videos.headline: Melrose: Being bad for so long is paying off for Panthers
videos.description: Barry Melrose discusses the reasons behind the Florida Panthers' 10-game winning streak, crediting Jaromir Jagr for his work with the team's young stars by saying, "he's teaching them how to work hard, how to be ready mentally for every game."
